{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":693,"text":"When you grow up in a developing country\nlike India, as I did,"},{"time":5754,"text":"you instantly learn to get more value\nfrom limited resources"},{"time":11107,"text":"and find creative ways to reuse\nwhat you already have."},{"time":16127,"text":"Take Mansukh Prajapati,\na potter in India."},{"time":20435,"text":"He has created a fridge\nmade entirely of clay"},{"time":25977,"text":"that consumes no electricity."},{"time":28275,"text":"He can keep fruits and vegetables\nfresh for many days."},{"time":32130,"text":"That's a cool invention, literally."},{"time":36680,"text":"In Africa, if you run out of\nyour cell phone battery, don't panic."},{"time":40906,"text":"You will find some\nresourceful entrepreneurs"},{"time":43920,"text":"who can recharge your \ncell phone using bicycles."},{"time":46565,"text":"And since we are in South America,"},{"time":48698,"text":"let's go to Lima in Peru,"},{"time":51842,"text":"a region with high humidity"},{"time":54466,"text":"that receives only one inch\nof rainfall each year."},{"time":59230,"text":"An engineering college in Lima\ndesigned a giant advertising billboard"},{"time":66124,"text":"that absorbs air humidity\nand converts it into purified water,"},{"time":72787,"text":"generating over 90 liters\nof water every day."},{"time":77664,"text":"The Peruvians are amazing."},{"time":79751,"text":"They can literally create\nwater out of thin air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84432,"text":"For the past seven years,"},{"time":86476,"text":"I have met and studied\nhundreds of entrepreneurs"},{"time":90252,"text":"in India, China, Africa and South America,\nand they keep amazing me."},{"time":96840,"text":"Many of them did not go to school."},{"time":100041,"text":"They don't invent stuff in big R&amp;D labs."},{"time":103517,"text":"The street is the lab."},{"time":107480,"text":"Why do they do that?"},{"time":109059,"text":"Because they don't have the kind\nof basic resources we take for granted,"},{"time":112526,"text":"like capital and energy,"},{"time":114367,"text":"and basic services\nlike healthcare and education"},{"time":117315,"text":"are also scarce in those regions."},{"time":120958,"text":"When external resources are scarce,\nyou have to go within yourself"},{"time":126945,"text":"to tap the most abundant\nresource, human ingenuity,"},{"time":130905,"text":"and use that ingenuity to find clever ways\nto solve problems with limited resources."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137700,"text":"In India, we call it Jugaad."},{"time":141986,"text":"Jugaad is a Hindi word"},{"time":144162,"text":"that means an improvised fix,\na clever solution born in adversity."},{"time":150190,"text":"Jugaad solutions are not\nsophisticated or perfect,"},{"time":154824,"text":"but they create more value at lower cost."},{"time":158353,"text":"For me, the entrepreneurs\nwho will create Jugaad solutions"},{"time":161812,"text":"are like alchemists."},{"time":163786,"text":"They can magically transform\nadversity into opportunity,"},{"time":167849,"text":"and turn something of less value\ninto something of high value."},{"time":173350,"text":"In other words, they mastered the art\nof doing more with less,"},{"time":180318,"text":"which is the essence of frugal innovation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185287,"text":"Frugal innovation is the ability \nto create more economic and social value"},{"time":190917,"text":"using fewer resources."},{"time":194277,"text":"Frugal innovation is not about making do;\nit's about making things better."},{"time":201238,"text":"Now I want to show you how,\nacross emerging markets,"},{"time":206210,"text":"entrepreneurs and companies are adopting \nfrugal innovation on a larger scale"},{"time":211109,"text":"to cost-effectively deliver healthcare\nand energy to billions of people"},{"time":215565,"text":"who may have little income\nbut very high aspirations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220960,"text":"Let's first go to China,"},{"time":223180,"text":"where the country's largest\nI.T. service provider, Neusoft,"},{"time":227197,"text":"has developed a telemedicine solution"},{"time":230030,"text":"to help doctors in cities\nremotely treat old and poor patients"},{"time":234722,"text":"in Chinese villages."},{"time":236553,"text":"This solution is based on\nsimple-to-use medical devices"},{"time":241198,"text":"that less qualified health workers\nlike nurses can use in rural clinics."},{"time":246355,"text":"China desperately needs\nthese frugal medical solutions"},{"time":250370,"text":"because by 2050 it will be home\nto over half a billion senior citizens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257568,"text":"Now let's go to Kenya,"},{"time":260516,"text":"a country where half the population\nuses M-Pesa, a mobile payment solution."},{"time":266507,"text":"This is a great solution\nfor the African continent"},{"time":269247,"text":"because 80 percent of Africans\ndon't have a bank account,"},{"time":273332,"text":"but what is exciting is that M-Pesa\nis now becoming the source"},{"time":278031,"text":"of other disruptive business models\nin sectors like energy."},{"time":282650,"text":"Take M-KOPA, the home solar solution\nthat comes literally in a box"},{"time":288468,"text":"that has a solar rooftop panel,\nthree LED lights,"},{"time":293463,"text":"a solar radio, and a cell phone charger."},{"time":296687,"text":"The whole kit, though, costs 200 dollars,\nwhich is too expensive for most Kenyans,"},{"time":302915,"text":"and this is where mobile telephony\ncan make the solution more affordable."},{"time":308858,"text":"Today, you can buy this kit by making\nan initial deposit of just 35 dollars,"},{"time":315011,"text":"and then pay off the rest by making\na daily micro-payment of 45 cents"},{"time":320398,"text":"using your mobile phone."},{"time":322790,"text":"Once you've made 365 micro-payments,\nthe system is unlocked,"},{"time":327713,"text":"and you own the product and you start \nreceiving clean, free electricity."},{"time":333958,"text":"This is an amazing solution for Kenya,"},{"time":336280,"text":"where 70 percent of people\nlive off the grid."},{"time":340940,"text":"This shows that with frugal innovation"},{"time":344128,"text":"what matters is that you take what is\nmost abundant, mobile connectivity,"},{"time":349120,"text":"to deal with what is scarce,\nwhich is energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354191,"text":"With frugal innovation,\nthe global South is actually catching up"},{"time":358761,"text":"and in some cases \neven leap-frogging the North."},{"time":362288,"text":"Instead of building expensive hospitals,\nChina is using telemedicine"},{"time":367480,"text":"to cost-effectively treat\nmillions of patients,"},{"time":371109,"text":"and Africa, instead of building\nbanks and electricity grids,"},{"time":375799,"text":"is going straight to mobile payments\nand distributed clean energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381116,"text":"Frugal innovation is diametrically opposed\nto the way we innovate in the North."},{"time":387875,"text":"I live in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":389521,"text":"where we keep chasing\nthe next big technology thing."},{"time":392934,"text":"Think of the iPhone 5, 6, then 7, 8."},{"time":397578,"text":"Companies in the West spend\nbillions of dollars investing in R&amp;D,"},{"time":401967,"text":"and use tons of natural resources\nto create ever more complex products,"},{"time":406431,"text":"to differentiate their brands\nfrom competition,"},{"time":409767,"text":"and they charge customers\nmore money for new features."},{"time":413854,"text":"So the conventional business model \nin the West is more for more."},{"time":421225,"text":"But sadly, this more for more model\nis running out of gas, for three reasons:"},{"time":426744,"text":"First, a big portion\nof customers in the West"},{"time":430890,"text":"because of the diminishing\npurchasing power,"},{"time":433872,"text":"can no longer afford\nthese expensive products."},{"time":436702,"text":"Second, we are running out of\nnatural water and oil."},{"time":441820,"text":"In California, where I live,\nwater scarcity is becoming a big problem."},{"time":445721,"text":"And third, most importantly,"},{"time":448338,"text":"because of the growing income disparity"},{"time":450713,"text":"between the rich \nand the middle class in the West,"},{"time":453773,"text":"there is a big disconnect\nbetween existing products and services"},{"time":457191,"text":"and basic needs of customers."},{"time":459372,"text":"Do you know that today,"},{"time":461270,"text":"there are over 70 million Americans\ntoday who are underbanked,"},{"time":466036,"text":"because existing banking services"},{"time":469358,"text":"are not designed to address\ntheir basic needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473616,"text":"The prolonged economic crisis\nin the West is making people think"},{"time":477508,"text":"that they are about to lose\nthe high standard of living"},{"time":480782,"text":"and face deprivation."},{"time":483638,"text":"I believe that the only way we can sustain\ngrowth and prosperity in the West"},{"time":488096,"text":"is if we learn to do more with less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491597,"text":"The good news is,\nthat's starting to happen."},{"time":494635,"text":"Several Western companies\nare now adopting frugal innovation"},{"time":498150,"text":"to create affordable products\nfor Western consumers."},{"time":502515,"text":"Let me give you two examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504945,"text":"When I first saw this building,"},{"time":506718,"text":"I told myself it's some\nkind of postmodern house."},{"time":509875,"text":"Actually, it's a small manufacturing plant\nset up by Grameen Danone,"},{"time":515123,"text":"a joint venture between \nGrameen Bank of Muhammad Yunus"},{"time":518579,"text":"and the food multinational Danone"},{"time":520515,"text":"to make high-quality yogurt in Bangladesh."},{"time":523830,"text":"This factory is 10 percent the size\nof existing Danone factories"},{"time":527774,"text":"and cost much less to build."},{"time":530536,"text":"I guess you can call it a low-fat factory."},{"time":534070,"text":"Now this factory, unlike Western factories\nthat are highly automated,"},{"time":538760,"text":"relies a lot on manual processes in order \nto generate jobs for local communities."},{"time":545493,"text":"Danone was so inspired by this model"},{"time":547769,"text":"that combines economic efficiency\nand social sustainability,"},{"time":551749,"text":"they are planning to roll it out\nin other parts of the world as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556121,"text":"Now, when you see this example,"},{"time":558123,"text":"you might be thinking, \"Well,\nfrugal innovation is low tech.\""},{"time":561917,"text":"Actually, no."},{"time":563560,"text":"Frugal innovation is also\nabout making high tech"},{"time":566782,"text":"more affordable and more\naccessible to more people."},{"time":569963,"text":"Let me give you an example."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571787,"text":"In China, the R&amp;D engineers\nof Siemens Healthcare"},{"time":574993,"text":"have designed a C.T. scanner\nthat is easy enough to be used"},{"time":579986,"text":"by less qualified health workers,\nlike nurses and technicians."},{"time":583709,"text":"This device can scan\nmore patients on a daily basis,"},{"time":587517,"text":"and yet consumes less energy,"},{"time":589792,"text":"which is great for hospitals,\nbut it's also great for patients"},{"time":593713,"text":"because it reduces the cost\nof treatment by 30 percent"},{"time":598406,"text":"and radiation dosage by up to 60 percent."},{"time":602052,"text":"This solution was initially designed\nfor the Chinese market,"},{"time":605674,"text":"but now it's selling like hotcakes\nin the U.S. and Europe,"},{"time":609691,"text":"where hospitals are pressured\nto deliver quality care at lower cost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616122,"text":"But the frugal innovation revolution"},{"time":618584,"text":"in the West is actually led\nby creative entrepreneurs"},{"time":622833,"text":"who are coming up with amazing solutions"},{"time":624992,"text":"to address basic needs\nin the U.S. and Europe."},{"time":628175,"text":"Let me quickly give you\nthree examples of startups"},{"time":631377,"text":"that personally inspire me."},{"time":633049,"text":"The first one happens to be launched\nby my neighbor in Silicon Valley."},{"time":636657,"text":"It's called gThrive."},{"time":638506,"text":"They make these wireless sensors\ndesigned like plastic rulers"},{"time":642337,"text":"that farmers can stick\nin different parts of the field"},{"time":645146,"text":"and start collecting detailed\ninformation like soil conditions."},{"time":649070,"text":"This dynamic data allows farmers\nto optimize use of water energy"},{"time":654085,"text":"while improving quality\nof the products and the yields,"},{"time":658335,"text":"which is a great solution for California,\nwhich faces major water shortage."},{"time":662964,"text":"It pays for itself within one year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665463,"text":"Second example is Be-Bound,\nalso in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":669108,"text":"that enables you\nto connect to the Internet"},{"time":671732,"text":"even in no-bandwidth areas\nwhere there's no wi-fi or 3G or 4G."},{"time":676681,"text":"How do they do that?"},{"time":678164,"text":"They simply use SMS, a basic technology,\nbut that happens to be the most reliable"},{"time":684568,"text":"and most widely available\naround the world."},{"time":686970,"text":"Three billion people today with \ncell phones can't access the Internet."},{"time":690280,"text":"This solution can connect them\nto the Internet in a frugal way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694788,"text":"And in France, there is\na startup calle Compte Nickel,"},{"time":698573,"text":"\nwhich is revolutionizing\nthe banking sector."},{"time":701174,"text":"It allows thousands of people\nto walk into a Mom and Pop store"},{"time":705167,"text":"and in just five minutes activate\nthe service that gives them two products:"},{"time":709486,"text":"an international bank account number\nand an international debit card."},{"time":713716,"text":"They charge a flat annual \nmaintenance fee of just 20 Euros."},{"time":718256,"text":"That means you can do\nall banking transactions --"},{"time":720558,"text":"send and receive money,\npay with your debit card --"},{"time":722953,"text":"all with no additional charge."},{"time":725321,"text":"This is what I call low-cost banking\nwithout the bank."},{"time":729222,"text":"Amazingly, 75 percent\nof the customers using this service"},{"time":733665,"text":"are the middle-class French\nwho can't afford high banking fees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738463,"text":"Now, I talked about frugal innovation,\ninitially pioneered in the South,"},{"time":742875,"text":"now being adopted in the North."},{"time":744965,"text":"Ultimately, we would like to see"},{"time":747333,"text":"developed countries\nand developing countries"},{"time":749678,"text":"come together and co-create\nfrugal solutions"},{"time":752743,"text":"that benefit the entire humanity."},{"time":755135,"text":"The exciting news is\nthat's starting to happen."},{"time":757923,"text":"Let's go to Nairobi to find that out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":760547,"text":"Nairobi has horrendous traffic jams."},{"time":764167,"text":"When I first saw them,\nI thought, \"Holy cow.\""},{"time":767082,"text":"Literally, because you have to dodge cows\nas well when you drive in Nairobi."},{"time":772258,"text":"To ease the situation,"},{"time":774186,"text":"the engineers at the IBM lab in Kenya\nare piloting a solution called Megaffic,"},{"time":780707,"text":"which initially was designed\nby the Japanese engineers."},{"time":785250,"text":"Unlike in the West, Megaffic\ndoesn't rely on roadside sensors,"},{"time":790424,"text":"which are very expensive\nto install in Nairobi."},{"time":792702,"text":"Instead they process images, traffic data,"},{"time":796397,"text":"collected from a small number of\nlow-resolution webcams in Nairobi streets,"},{"time":802026,"text":"and then they use analytic software\nto predict congestion points,"},{"time":806216,"text":"and they can SMS drivers\nalternate routes to take."},{"time":810117,"text":"Granted, Megaffic is not\nas sexy as self-driving cars,"},{"time":814459,"text":"but it promises to take Nairobi drivers\nfrom point A to point B"},{"time":819446,"text":"at least 20 percent faster."},{"time":822696,"text":"And earlier this year, UCLA Health\nlaunched its Global Lab for Innovation,"},{"time":829412,"text":"which seeks to identify frugal healthcare \nsolutions anywhere in the world"},{"time":834087,"text":"that will be at least 20 percent cheaper\nthan existing solutions in the U.S."},{"time":839474,"text":"and yet more effective."},{"time":841584,"text":"It also tries to bring together\ninnovators from North and South"},{"time":846339,"text":"to cocreate affordable healthcare\nsolutions for all of humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852027,"text":"I gave tons of examples of frugal\ninnovators from around the world,"},{"time":856300,"text":"but the question is, how do you go about\nadopting frugal innovation?"},{"time":860328,"text":"Well, I gleaned out three principles\nfrom frugal innovators around the world"},{"time":863923,"text":"that I want to share with you"},{"time":865669,"text":"that you can apply\nin your own organization"},{"time":867940,"text":"to do more with less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":870649,"text":"The first principle is: Keep it simple."},{"time":874829,"text":"Don't create solutions\nto impress customers."},{"time":877870,"text":"Make them easy enough to use\nand widely accessible,"},{"time":881121,"text":"like the C.T. scanner we saw in China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884128,"text":"Second principle: \nDo not reinvent the wheel."},{"time":888319,"text":"Try to leverage existing resources\nand assets that are widely available,"},{"time":892405,"text":"like using mobile telephony\nto offer clean energy"},{"time":896399,"text":"or Mom and Pop stores\nto offer banking services."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900091,"text":"Third principle is:\nThink and act horizontally."},{"time":904381,"text":"Companies tend to scale up vertically"},{"time":907567,"text":"by centralizing operations\nin big factories and warehouses,"},{"time":911097,"text":"but if you want to be agile and deal\nwith immense customer diversity,"},{"time":915253,"text":"you need to scale out horizontally\nusing a distributed supply chain"},{"time":920052,"text":"with smaller manufacturing\nand distribution units,"},{"time":922906,"text":"like Grameen Bank has shown."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927164,"text":"The South pioneered frugal innovation\nout of sheer necessity."},{"time":932379,"text":"The North is now learning to do\nmore and better with less"},{"time":936684,"text":"as it faces resource constraints."},{"time":939958,"text":"As an Indian-born French national\nwho lives in the United States,"},{"time":945321,"text":"my hope is that we transcend\nthis artificial North-South divide"},{"time":951702,"text":"so that we can harness\nthe collective ingenuity"},{"time":954043,"text":"of innovators from around the world"},{"time":956397,"text":"to cocreate frugal solutions"},{"time":959021,"text":"that will improve the quality of life\nof everyone in the world,"},{"time":963479,"text":"while preserving our precious planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966358,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968448,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}